# Point as a 2-element Vec; distance squared.
*dist2(a as Vec of i64, b as Vec of i64) returns i64
    dx is a.get(0) - b.get(0)
    dy is a.get(1) - b.get(1)
    dx * dx + dy * dy

*mkpt(x as i64, y as i64) returns Vec of i64
    p is vec()
    p.push(x)
    p.push(y)
    p

*main
    a is mkpt(0, 0)
    b is mkpt(3, 4)
    log dist2(a, b)
